MAPLight,org,performs,research,on,supporting,and,opposing,interests,for,legislative,bills,MAPLight,org,s,Bill,Positions,API,provides,a,tool,for,discovering,the,connection,between,campaign,donations,and,legislative,votes,It,can,also,be,mashed,up,with,other,databases,that,contain,information,about,bills,or,politically,active,organizations,This,RESTful,API,returns,results,in,JSON,or,XML